museum_dirgantara_nasional_amerika_serikat
museum_dirgantara_nasional_amerika_serikat adalah sebuah museum yang terletak di washington , d.c . , amerika_serikat dan membuka bangunan_utamanya pada tahun 1976 .
museum ini merupakan bagian dari yayasan_smithsonian .
pada museum ini , terdapat koleksi terbesar pesawat terbang dan pesawat_angkasa .
museum ini juga pusat yang vital untuk penelitian_sejarah , ilmu_pengetahuan dan teknologi_penerbangan dan penerbangan_luar_angkasa , dan juga pengetahuan_planet dan geologi dan geofisika .
pada bagian utama museum , termasuk diantaranya terdapat 61 pesawat terbang , 51 artefak_luar_angkasa yang besar , dan lebih dari 2.000 item yang lebih kecil pada tanggal 1 juni 2007 .
humpuss_intermoda_transportasi
pt . humpuss_intermoda_transportasi_tbk merupakan perusahaan_publik yang bergerak dalam bidang_transportasi dan bermarkas di jakarta , indonesia .
perusahaan ini didirikan pada tahun 1977 .
hits have 6 business_structure , they_are lng , petrochemical_and_oil , offshore , mining_bulk , crewing_management_services_and_agency .
hits_is not a big company , but a_good_company_in_the niche_market .
business
lng_carrier
lng_carrier_business_was_conducted_by a subsidiary within_hits_group .
operating_the_lng_ekaputra , the_company_also_manages 3 ships_owned_by_other_parties .
ekaputra_is_an lng_tanker_with a length_of 290 meters_and a size_of_78.988_dwt , built_by_mitsubishi_heavy_industries_ltd . in_nagasaki , japan , and_had_been_chartered_by_pt . pertamina_since_january_10 , 1990 .
hits_believed , the_implementation_of_regular_maintenance_programs_in_accordance_with_industry_'s_standards , including_docking , will_ensured_the_quality_and_reliability_of_the_ekaputra .
petrochemical &_oil_carrier
petrochemical and_oil_carrier_managed_by pt . htk .
the_fact_that_indonesia_'s_chemical_industry_is_growing_rapidly , which_makes_petrochemical a potential market , is_unavoidable .
this condition_caused an increase_in_petrochemical_vessels_demand .
it_is_an opportunity_that_needs_to_be_taken_by pt . htk_in_years_to_come_by_providing_larger_fleets_specialized_to_transport_chemical_around_the_country .
units_of_oil_carrier_have_dwt_ranging from 1.300 to_18.000_metric_tons .
pt . htk_focused_its_business_on_improving_the_quality_of_transportation_services , including_service_quality_and_safety_aspects .
all oil_tankers_owned_by pt . htk_have_obtained a time_charter_contract_with pt . pertamina_for a charter_period_of_between 1 and 2 years , including_extension_options .
pt . htk_has_obtain_certification_of_iso_9001 :_2008_and_ohsas_18001 : 2007 from_bureu_veritas_for_management_service_for_ship_and_offshore_shipping , ship_chartering_and_marketing_services .
offshore &_harbor support_vessel
one_of pt . htk_'s_subsidiaries_also_manages_the_business_line_of offshore and_harbour_support_vessels .
currently , this line_of_business_consist_of_harbour_tugs_and_mooring_boat_management .
as support_vessels , harbour_tugs_and_mooring_boats_have_the_main_function_of_assisting_the_process_of_mooring_and_releasing_lng_carriers_to_and_from_fsru .
mining_bulk_carrier
the bulk_carrier_business_line_is_managed_by pt . htc , managing_19_sets_of_tugs_and_barges .
in_running_its_operation , pt . htc always prioritizing optimal services_from_preparation_to_ready-made_fleet .
pt . htc_also_has a market_orientation_which_features a time_charter_contract_scheme_rather_than_spot_charter .
pt . htc_has_become_the regional leader_in_industrial_tugs_and_barges , ship_'s agency_and_crew_management .
pt . htc_focuses_on_servicing_beyond_costumer_satisfaction_by_offering an integrated_shipping_solution_services_supported_by_qualified_and_reliable_vessels , crews , systems_and_management .
crewing_management_services
crew management_services_is_managed_by pt . mcs_internasional .
pt . mcsi_is a unit under_the_supervision_of pt . htc , in_the_field_of_ship_manning_services_and_crew_training_services .
along_with_the_continued_increase_in_the_national_merchant_fleet , the_shipping_prospects_extended_to_be_promising_with_the_increasing_demand_for_ship_'s_crews .
at_this_moment , the_growth_of_seafarers_is_not_yet_balanced_with_vessels .
services_of_providing and_managing_crew_possessing_good_quality_and_personality_for_ships_are a niche_market that_currently_is_still a_wide-open_door_in_the_shipping_industry , for_which , reliability_in_the_process_of_recruiting , screening , selecting_and_procuring_the_crews_is_required .
crew_management_does_not_stop_in_procurement , but_also_do_ship_operations , maintenance , insurance , surveys , repairs , purchases_of_logistics_and_other_things_needed_in_the_operation_of_the_ship .
pt . mcsi_as_the_manning_agent_has_been_successfully_certified_and_registered_under_class nk for_the_following_international_standards_rules_required_as_under_iso_9001 : 2008 for_the_quality_management_system , statement_of_compliance_for_mlc_2006_and_seafarer_'s_recruitment &_placement_service_providers .
training_centre_managed_by_pt . mcsi_to_be_operated_in_cooperation_with_trilogi university .
with_the_support_from_trilogi university , located_in a strategic_place , pt . mcsi_believes_training_centre_will be_able_to_develop_as_much_as_possible_in_order_to_build_the_competency_and_proficiency_of_the_crews .
the_instructors_having_experiences_in lng_vessels_have been_well_trained_by_tot_imo_model_course_6.09_conducted by_human_resource_development_of transportation_agency_of_ministry_of_transportation .
company_has_developed_soft_skill_training_center_since 7_october_2009 .
the_purpose is_to_improve_crew_competitiveness_in_regard_to_communication , problem solving_and_leadership .
soft_skill_is_divided_into_three level : basic , intermediate_and_advance .
simulation_games_and_focus_group_discussion_are_given_to_the_participants_previously_defined_by_the_trainee_and_has_been_customized_to_the_needs_of_customers .
